&lt;li&gt;云上解决方案&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title/><link>https://dlliang14.github.io/web-publicNotes/k8s-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dlliang14.github.io/web-publicNotes/k8s-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="k8s-部署-常用工具"&gt;
 k8s-部署-常用工具
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#k8s-%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%b2-%e5%b8%b8%e7%94%a8%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="集群部署常用工具"&gt;
 集群部署常用工具
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%e9%9b%86%e7%be%a4%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%b2%e5%b8%b8%e7%94%a8%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
